#CircuitBreakerSG D-54

Knowing how much we miss having Dim Sum, dearest Sis @xiaoqing1200 personally delivered some from @tiongbahru.pau last night. #feelingloved
🌸 Char Siew Pau
🌸 Da Pau
🌸 Siew Mai
🌸 Lo Mai Kai
🌸 Fan Choy

There are more in the fridge and we're indulging in some Dim Sum Breakfast this weekend. 飲杯茶食個包

@sincerelyaline Yay... weekend brunch is supposed to be like this 🤗
My idea of a good breakfast/ brunch 👌👌
Love that da bao and char siu bao Yvonne 😍
@make.happyy Love those too, so blessed to receive 😍
We were gifted the Char Siew Pau a few weeks ago. It was my fave eat, together with the Lo Mai Kai. ❤️
@jane_wu Thanks Jane. Yay... surrounded by lovely sisters 😍
😍Absolutely all time favourite! 😍you got a lovely sis too
